cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY 

This paper presents a self-supervised imitation learning scheme using deep reinforcement learning and inverse dynamics models. The focus is on robotic arm and hand manipulation tasks, which suggests the paper may fall under the robotics (cs.RO) or computer vision (cs.CV) categories. However, the use of deep reinforcement learning and inverse dynamics models also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper proposes a reward structure to ensure effective learning, which suggests a focus on control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.RO, followed by cs.CV and cs.SY.
